# Web — React (Feature-based + Hooks)

Patrón obligatorio. Principios globales: `engineering-standards.mdc`.

## Capas (flujo unidireccional)

```
Page  →  Hook (TanStack Query)  →  API client  →  Backend REST
  ↓
Components (UI pura, props in / events out)
```

| Capa | Carpeta | Responsabilidad |
|------|---------|-----------------|
| **Page** | `pages/` | Layout, compone componentes, sin fetch directo |
| **Feature** | `features/` | Agrupa page + hooks + components por dominio (opcional) |
| **Hook** | `hooks/` | Fetch, cache, loading/error — `useEvaluation`, `useHitlQueue` |
| **API** | `api/` | **Único** punto HTTP tipado |
| **Component** | `components/` | UI reutilizable; props tipadas, sin lógica de negocio |
| **Types** | `types/` | Espejo de DTOs backend (`EvaluationResult`) |
| **Lib** | `lib/` | formatters, constants — funciones puras |

## Estructura

```
web/src/
├── pages/                # Dashboard, Transactions, Evaluate, HITL, Audit
├── features/             # evaluations/, hitl/, audit/ (opcional)
├── components/           # DecisionBadge, AgentTimeline, DataTable
├── hooks/                # useEvaluation, useTransactions, useHitlQueue
├── api/
│   └── client.ts         # getEvaluation(), resolveHitl(), etc.
├── types/
│   └── evaluation.ts
├── lib/                  # formatCurrency, formatDate, decisionColors
└── App.tsx
```

## Reglas por capa

- **Pages**: usan hooks; no `fetch()` inline ni lógica de fraude
- **Hooks**: TanStack Query; exponen `{ data, isLoading, error, mutate }`
- **API client**: base URL desde `VITE_API_URL`; tipos de retorno explícitos
- **Components**: presentacionales; badges, tablas, timelines sin side effects
- **Sin Redux** — estado servidor en TanStack Query; UI local en `useState`
- **Comments**: English only (`//`, JSDoc)
- **UI language**: **English only** — labels, headings, buttons, empty/error states, placeholders (see `engineering-standards.mdc`)

## Páginas obligatorias

Dashboard | Transacciones | Evaluación | Cola HITL | Audit trail

## Ejemplo correcto

```tsx
// page — solo compone
export function EvaluatePage() {
  const { id } = useParams();
  const { data, isLoading, error } = useEvaluation(id!);
  if (isLoading) return <Loading />;
  if (error) return <ErrorState error={error} />;
  return <EvaluationDetail evaluation={data} />;
}

// hook — lógica de datos
export function useEvaluation(txId: string) {
  return useQuery({ queryKey: ["evaluation", txId], queryFn: () => api.getEvaluation(txId) });
}
```

## Stack

React 18, Vite, TypeScript, Tailwind, TanStack Query, React Router.

## UX

Badges por decisión, timeline agentes, barra confidence, mobile-first (tablas → cards).

## Tests

`web-testing.mdc` — MSW mock API; testear 4 estados UI por page.

## Prohibido

Lógica de agentes, LLM o reglas de fraude en el frontend.
